Pound Weakens Versus Dollar After U.K. Inflation Accelerates

-- B y   L u c y   M e a k i n
-- 
2011-10-18T08:42:34Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-18/pound-weakens-versus-dollar-after-u-k-inflation-accelerates.html
The pound weakened versus the
dollar, reversing an earlier 0.5 percent advance, after
inflation accelerated to match a record high in September.  Sterling declined 0.2 percent to $1.5713 as of 9:38 a.m. in
 London . The pound was 0.3 percent stronger against the euro at
87.00 pence.  Consumer prices rose 5.2 percent from a year earlier,
compared with 4.5 percent in August, the  Office for National
Statistics  said in London today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Lucy Meakin in London at 
 lmeakin1@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
